//  @file
//  BiosGuard Update Script Language file for BIOS region update.
//
//  DO NOT MODIFY THIS FILE.
//
//  NOTE:
//    (1) Set up BIOS offset and length to be updated.
//    (2) Script that erases F0 and writes all the flash from B0 and
//        allowing a max of 3 write and 3 erase errors.
//    (3) The flash size is dynamically calculated based FLREG1 Region
//        Base and Limit Erase block size is 4KB.
//    (4) Return values set in If
//        - Return 0 = Success
//        - Return 1 = Erase errors > 3
//        - Return 2 = Write errors > 3
//
